item.title: Demo 01 – Contact us
item.dc:creator: bitwallas@yahoo.com
item.content:encoded:
Contact us

Homey supports Contact Form 7. With this plugin can manage multiple contact forms, plus you can customize the form and the mail contents flexibly with simple markup. The form supports Ajax-powered submitting, CAPTCHA, Akismet spam filtering and so on.

[contact-form-7 id="1343" title="Contact form 1"]

Corporate Office

7652 Washington Avenue, Suite 315, Miami Beach, FL 33139

Direct Contact

Phone: 800 987 6543
Toll-Free: 800 987 1234
Email: homey@email.com

Company Deparment

To contact our team, please select one of the following:

Sales
Careers
Disputes
Help
